#: src\runtimes/typescript.md:15
msgid "Usage (Node)"
msgstr "使い方（Node）"

#: src\runtimes/typescript.md:17
msgid ""
"On Node, the runtime auto-spawns a [`sahou "
"link`](../networking-and-deployment.md) if none is running."
msgstr "Node では、link が動いていなければランタイムが [`sahou link`](../networking-and-deployment.md) を自動的に起動します。"

#: src\runtimes/typescript.md:20
msgid ""
"```ts\n"
"import { connect } from \"sahou\";\n"
"\n"
"const node = await connect(\"gen/descriptor.json\", { node: \"visuals\" });\n"
"\n"
"await node.subscribe(\"touch\", (p) => { /* ... */ }, {\n"
"  onReject: (code, detail) => { /* a boundary NO lands here, not in the "
"handler */ },\n"
"});\n"
"await node.publish(\"cue\", { /* ... */ });          // send-boundary NO → "
"SahouRejected\n"
"const res = await node.queryConfirmed(\"get_state\", { /* ... */ }, { "
"retries: 3 });\n"
"await node.answer(\"get_state\", async (req) => ({ level: 3 }));\n"
"await node.close();\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

